1217
01:24:37,202 --> 01:24:38,661
Williamstown.

1218
01:24:38,662 --> 01:24:41,467
Verão de 76.

1219
01:24:41,707 --> 01:24:44,083
A sua primeira peça.

1220
01:24:44,084 --> 01:24:46,599
Que desastre!

1221
01:24:47,212 --> 01:24:49,547
